JavaLog.visitor
Class Visitor

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--JavaLog.visitor.Visitor
Direct Known Subclasses:
TransformerVisitor
public abstract class Visitor
extends java.lang.Object

This is the Visitor component of the Visitor design pattern. This class represents an abstract operation performed on the elements of the PlObject hierarcy. This class lets you to define a new operation without changing the classes of the elements on which it operates.
